    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      bearerCORE™ bridges the physical familiarity of banknotes with the security and programmability of digital infrastructure — giving Central Banks full monetary sovereignty without requiring consumers or commercial banks to manage cryptographic key material.
    </p>
